    "-AI engineer-[G24].",
    "Some external causes of AI system unpredictability were also discussed by a few participants in a study [G1] such as cyber-security threats.",
    "Likewise, clients' needs such as profit maximisation and attention optimisation were mentioned as one of the causes of unpredictable system behavior that ultimately develops ethical issues.",
    "A participant in a study [G7] stated: ɓ \"It's not that we thought what we were doing was safe, it's just that, certain inbuilt desires to increase clicks, to increase attention, to maximise advertising was our primary motivation.",
    "You did not have to think about any other consequences.\""
